sql:
SELECT MIN(revenue) AS minimum_revenue
FROM conversions
WHERE payment_status = 'completed';

external_knowledge:
- CTR (Click-through Rate) is a measure of the number of clicks advertisers receive on their ads per number of impressions; 
- Conversion rate refers to the proportion of users who complete a desired action after clicking on a link; 
- Commission rates are the rates at which advertisers pay for conversions or clicks on their affiliate links.

